    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>To make, arrange, compose, or construct a written work, art work, or other work, by arrangement of materials collected from various sources. It may refer to the arrangement of content only (as in a literary work), or of physical pieces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
